{"tid":2023870,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"What if... John Wick遇上陳浩南","createTime":"2020-05-19T09:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:24:10.000Z","uid":164163,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b4df0773edd24cbde3e5c07162e4191c44f12f","tid":2023870,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"(以下ff情節)<br />\n<br />\n某日 John Wick嚟香港旅行 仲帶埋心愛嘅狗 目的係沖淡情傷(詳情請睇JW1) 去咗銅鑼灣酒吧消遣 點知浩南好兄弟山雞無啦啦殺咗人隻狗 之後JW盛嬲之下對冧咗山雞 陳浩南嬲到即刻殺去JW度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7fdU9K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7fdU9K.jpg&h=86855d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ToLmjBq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FToLmjBq.jpg&h=bae8f04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個男人 有著相似嘅背景,經歷  究竟邊個可以企到最後?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(sorry 我真係好鍾意ff唔同嘅電影人物相遇 希望有同樣諗法嘅ching可以一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"c2f603a4d2159f2740cd8473278743c0f0d4585b","tid":2023870,"uid":75164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"南哥同山雞條ex 扑過嘢<br />\n冇JW 品格咁好喎 邊有得比"},{"pid":"089372bc6fe5ab507c9e2b3eec42eedf7ccc872f","tid":2023870,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"黑社會點同職業殺手鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32877aaf7d0ed8e7241205338e0050c70da73fb8","tid":2023870,"uid":353256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"john wick係殺神，陳浩南打爛仔交，個人認為john wick秒殺陳浩南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cc25d8ec22a3274a738c4